description:
Create ralph-logs/src/app.ts — the top-level application component with a three-panel layout using OpenTUI.

## OpenTUI API reference
OpenTUI is a Bun-only TUI framework. Key APIs:

```typescript
import { createCliRenderer, Box, Text, ScrollBox } from '@opentui/core'

// Create renderer
const renderer = await createCliRenderer({ exitOnCtrlC: true })

// Box: container with flexbox layout
// Props: width, height (number or '%'), flexDirection ('row'|'column'),
//   flexGrow (number), borderStyle ('single'|'rounded'|'double'|'heavy'),
//   padding (number), gap (number), bg (hex string)
// Usage: Box(props, ...children) returns a node
// Add to renderer: renderer.root.add(node)

// Text: simple text display
// Props: content (string), fg (hex), bg (hex), bold (boolean), dim (boolean),
//   italic (boolean), inverse (boolean)
// Usage: Text({ content: 'hello', bold: true })

// ScrollBox: scrollable container
// Props: scrollY (boolean), scrollX (boolean), stickyScroll ('bottom'|'top'),
//   width, height, flexGrow
// Methods: scrollBy({ y: N }), scrollTo({ y: N })
```

## Layout structure
```
Root Box (flexDirection: 'column', width: '100%', height: '100%')
├── Main Box (flexDirection: 'row', flexGrow: 1)
│   ├── Sidebar Box (width: 25, borderStyle: 'single')
│   │   └── Text('Sidebar')  [placeholder]
│   └── Content Box (flexGrow: 1)
│       └── Text('Content')  [placeholder]
└── Status Bar Box (height: 1, width: '100%')
    └── Text('Status bar')  [placeholder, inverse: true]
```

## Import
Import SIDEBAR_WIDTH (=25) from './constants.ts'.

## Export
`async function createApp(): Promise<{ renderer, sidebarBox, contentBox, statusBarBox }>`

Returns references to the three panel Box nodes so other modules can populate them.

## Update main.ts
Replace the console.log with:
```typescript
import { createApp } from './app.ts'
await createApp()
```

## Important notes
- The sidebar should have a visible right border to separate from content. Use borderStyle: 'single' on the sidebar Box. If OpenTUI doesn't support per-side borders, use a full border on the sidebar box.
- Status bar should use inverse styling (reverse video). Set inverse: true on the Text inside it, or use bg/fg to simulate.
- All boxes should fill available space. Main box gets flexGrow: 1. Content box gets flexGrow: 1.
